@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_diqmtj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.25
    v0 = (0.64 * wp.exp((tmp + 0.11 + tmp + 0.83)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(tmp) / (wp.cos(tmp + 0.43) + v0))
    v2 = wp.exp((0.45 - v1))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.98) / 0.35) * ((tmp + 0.38 - v1 + 0.23) * (v0 + 0.51 + v0 + 0.95)))
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
